snippet.title: Dweep - First 10 Levels of Gameplay
snippet.description:
【I apologize for the flickering picture of this video, it seems there is a problem with my operating system running a game in compatible mode】
This is an oldie game that I first knew by watching my dad play, later on when I learned how to read I picked this game up and enjoyed it a lot.
